'''Cha''' aka Chanoir is a graffiti artist based in , .  He was born in  and raised in  where he began his graffiti.  He is best known for his eponymous cat character, Cha. "Over time, his cats began to take on their own personalities and went on from the Parisian streets to become famous on the Barcelona graffiti scene."<ref name="streetart">Street Art: The Spray Files, HarperCollins, 2004, p.180</ref>
